利亚姆·佩恩去世后，盖伊·钱伯斯呼吁音乐产业停止让青少年加入流行乐队https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death- 3804414?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=guy-chambers-呼吁音乐行业停止在利亚姆-佩恩斯死亡之后将青少年加入流行音乐团体Laura MolloySun, 20 Oct 2024 10:18:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3804414 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我建议人们在 18 岁之前不应该加入男孩乐队，整个行业也应该坚持这一点”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">盖伊·钱伯斯 (Guy Chambers) 在利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 去世后呼吁音乐行业停止让青少年加入流行乐队的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Guy-Chambers-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Jesse-Wild_Guitarist-Magazine_Future-via-Getty-Images-and-Anthony-Harvey_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩</a>去世后，歌曲作家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guy-chambers">盖伊·钱伯斯</a>呼吁音乐行业停止让未成年人加入男孩乐队。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="593" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755"><b>利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 1993-2024：One Direction 明星帮助引发了流行现象</b></a></li></ul><p>这位独唱艺术家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>成员于周三（10 月 16 日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落</a>身亡，享年 31 岁。</p><p>自他去世以来，来自音乐界的人士纷纷谈论名气对年轻明星的影响。佩恩第一次参加<em>《X Factor》</em>试镜时年仅 14 岁，在节目第 10 季期间成为 One Direction 成员时年仅 16 岁。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯 (Robbie Williams)</a>也是悼念者之一，他说佩恩作为前男孩乐队成员所经历的“考验和磨难与我的经历非常相似”。这位前 Take That 主唱 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-opens-up-about-past-self-harming-3528952">此前曾公开讲述过他的自残和抑郁史</a>，并鼓励人们对自己在公众眼中发表的评论更加“谨慎”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803908" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803908" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803908" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1.jpg" alt="2011 年 3 月 7 日，One Direction 的 Zayn Malik、Harry Styles、Liam Payne、Louis Tomlinson 和 Niall Horan 在 HMV 在英国曼彻斯特签署了他们的新书《One Direction：永远年轻：我们的官方 X-Factor 故事》。 （摄影：Shirlaine Forrest/WireImage）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-posing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803908" class="wp-caption-text"> 2011 年 3 月 7 日，One Direction 的 Zayn Malik、Harry Styles、Liam Payne、Louis Tomlinson 和 Niall Horan 在 HMV 在英国曼彻斯特签署了他们的新书《One Direction：永远年轻：我们的官方 X-Factor 故事》。 （摄影：Shirlaine Forrest/WireImage）</figcaption></figure><p>现在，与威廉姆斯密切合作制作了《天使》和《让我娱乐你》等热门歌曲的钱伯斯反思了佩恩年轻时的巨大名气。 “我确实认为让一个 16 岁的孩子进入这样的成人世界可能会造成真正的伤害。罗比（威廉姆斯）当然经历过这一点，”他告诉<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/business/2024/oct/20/dont-let-under-18s-join-pop-bands-says-leading-songwriter-after-liam-paynes-death" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>观察家报</em></a>。</p><p>他继续说道：“我有四个孩子，所以我经常考虑这个问题。我知道在罗比的案例中，Take That 并没有设立任何适当的保护措施来照顾十几岁的男孩。那是很久以前的事了，但我没有看到太多改变的迹象。据我观察，参与大型电视选秀节目的人们并没有给予更多真正的关心。”</p><p>钱伯斯接着表示，行业应该考虑引入新的规定：“我建议人们在 18 岁之前不应该加入男孩乐队，行业也应该遵守这一点。”</p><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Sharon-Osbourne">莎朗·奥斯本</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-accuses-music-industry-of-letting-down-liam-payne-3803983">指责音乐产业“让佩恩失望”</a> ，她在 Instagram 上发帖写道：“利亚姆，我的心很痛。我们都让你失望了。当你需要他们的时候这个行业在哪里？当你进入世界上最艰难的行业之一时，你还只是个孩子。谁在你的角落里？安息吧我的朋友”</p><p>奥斯本向佩恩致敬之前，与 One Direction 一起参加选秀节目的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Katie-Waissel">凯蒂·威塞尔 (Katie Waissel)</a>发表评论， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katie-waissel-calls-for-more-care-and-support-for-young-artists-after-death-of-liam-payne-the-focus-remained-on-profits-rather-than-the-people-3803888">呼吁更多“对年轻艺术家的关心和支持</a>”。同样，在同一季节目中获得第二名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rebecca-ferguson-speaks-out-on-exploitation-and-profiteering-of-young-stars-in-liam-payne-tribute-3803708">在向佩恩致敬的同时，也公开反对“对年轻明星的剥削和牟取暴利”。</a></p><p>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀还表示，佩恩去世后，音乐产业“给年轻人带来了巨大的压力”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Victoria-Canal">维多利亚·卡纳尔</a>则表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">作为一名“绝望”想要实现佩恩曾经取得的成功的艺术家，感觉被“欺骗”了。这个行业‘成功’的承诺是什么。”</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3803758" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803758" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803758" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-400x267.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-696x464.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-1068x712.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803758" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩 图片来源：Mike Marsland/Mike Marsland/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> One Direction 的幸存成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">扎恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">本周早些时候就佩恩的去世发表了一份联合声明，他们在声明中表达了悲痛，并表示他们需要时间“哀悼并处理失去我们兄弟的痛苦”。我们深爱着。”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-fans-hold-vigils-for-liam-payne-in-liverpool-3804346">世界各地也出现了球迷为佩恩守夜的活动，包括在他去世的利物浦</a>和阿根廷。本周早些时候，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-father-reads-fan-tributes-outside-argentinian-hotel-where-he-died-3804283">父亲杰夫加入了卡萨苏尔酒店外的人群</a>，感谢聚集在一起纪念他儿子的粉丝。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">在整个音乐界，其他人都向佩恩表示了敬意</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shawn-mendes-dedicates-heart-of-gold-to-liam-payne-3804271">肖恩·门德斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-maggie-rogers-pay-tribute-to-liam-payne-with-tender-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3804224">玛吉·罗杰斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-performs-tearful-liam-payne-duet-hours-after-his-death-3803926">丽塔·奥拉</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-comments-on-liam-paynes-death-life-is-precious-3803700">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>。</p><p>佩恩的前伴侣、佩恩 7 岁儿子贝尔的母亲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cheryl-cole">谢丽尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cheryl-indescribably-painful-death-liam-payne-please-give-liam-little-dignity-he-has-left-3804228">公开讲述了这一“难以形容的痛苦”损失</a>，并敦促人们“给予利亚姆仅存的一点尊严”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">盖伊·钱伯斯 (Guy Chambers) 在利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 去世后呼吁音乐行业停止让青少年加入流行乐队的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
