利亚姆·佩恩去世后，One Direction 赢得了有史以来最大的流媒体日https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-earn-biggest-streaming-day-of-all-time-following-liam-paynes-death-3804388?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=one-继利亚姆·佩恩斯死亡之后，方向赚取最大的流媒体日Laura MolloySun, 20 Oct 2024 08:48:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3804388 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队的其余成员本周早些时候向佩恩表示敬意，称他们需要时间“哀悼并处理失去我们深爱的兄弟”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-earn-biggest-streaming-day-of-all-time-following-liam-paynes-death-3804388">利亚姆·佩恩去世后，《One Direction》的帖子创下了有史以来流媒体播放量最高的一天，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/One-Direction-in-2013.-CREDIT_-Toni-Anne-Barson_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">Liam Payne</a>周三（10 月 16 日）去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>实现了迄今为止最大的流媒体日。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>佩恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落身亡，</a>年仅 31 岁。据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/oct/17/liam-payne-died-of-multiple-traumas-and-internal-and-external-bleeding" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道，阿根廷检察官办公室透露，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。</p><p> One Direction 的幸存成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">扎恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">本周早些时候就佩恩的去世发表了一份联合声明，他们在声明中表达了悲痛，并表示他们需要时间“哀悼并处理失去我们兄弟的痛苦”。我们深爱着。”</a></p><p>自从佩恩不幸去世后，随着粉丝们追忆开启他职业生涯的歌曲，他的前乐队的音乐在流媒体排行榜上不断攀升。据<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBUfmzqTnDh/?igsh=OXA5azIwMmpqazJv&amp;img_index=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Complex</em></a>报道，10 月 17 日，他们的音乐在全球范围内获得了 5750 万次流媒体播放，这是他们迄今为止在流媒体平台上取得的最高数字。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/conormurray/2024/10/18/one-direction-hits-no-2-artist-on-global-spotify-chart-after-liam-paynes-death/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《福布斯》</em></a>报道，该男孩乐队目前是英国 Spotify 排名第一的艺人和全球排名第二的艺人，仅次于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> )。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">利物浦利亚姆·佩恩守夜：哀悼者静静地唱着 One Direction 的《我一生的故事》 <a href="https://t.co/gzXC6az0m9">pic.twitter.com/gzXC6az0m9</a></p><p> - Con Corner (@ConCorner23) <a href="https://twitter.com/ConCorner23/status/1847634490908168607?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 19 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>该乐队 2014 年专辑《Four》中的热门单曲《Night Changes》一直是播放次数最多的歌曲之一，在 Spotify 每日全球歌曲排行榜上以超过 460 万次播放量上升至第六位，并成为 TikTok 热门歌曲中的第六位。</p><p>其他重新进入 Spotify 排行榜的歌曲包括“Story of My Life”、“What Makes You Beautiful”和“Perfect”。</p><p>此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-fans-hold-vigils-for-liam-payne-in-liverpool-3804346">，世界各地的球迷都在为佩恩守夜，其中包括利物浦</a>和他去世的阿根廷。本周早些时候，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-father-reads-fan-tributes-outside-argentinian-hotel-where-he-died-3804283">父亲杰夫加入了卡萨苏尔酒店外的人群</a>，感谢聚集在一起纪念他儿子的粉丝。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">在整个音乐界，其他人都向佩恩表示了敬意</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shawn-mendes-dedicates-heart-of-gold-to-liam-payne-3804271">肖恩·门德斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-maggie-rogers-pay-tribute-to-liam-payne-with-tender-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3804224">玛吉·罗杰斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-the-struggles-of-liam-payne-his-trials-and-tribulations-were-very-similar-to-mine-3804014">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-performs-tearful-liam-payne-duet-hours-after-his-death-3803926">丽塔·奥拉</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-comments-on-liam-paynes-death-life-is-precious-3803700">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">维多利亚·卡纳尔</a>。</p><p>佩恩的前伴侣、佩恩 7 岁儿子贝尔的母亲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cheryl-cole">谢丽尔</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cheryl-indescribably-painful-death-liam-payne-please-give-liam-little-dignity-he-has-left-3804228">公开讲述了这一“难以形容的痛苦”损失</a>，并敦促人们“给予利亚姆仅存的一点尊严”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-cassidy-girlfriend-of-liam-payne-pays-tribute-i-will-continue-to-love-you-for-the-rest-of-my-life-3804236">佩恩去世时的女友凯特·卡西迪也公开表示</a>：“我完全不知所措。过去几天的一切都感觉不到真实。我请求并祈祷你能给我恩典和空间来私下解决这个问题。”</p><p>其他消息方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zayn-malik-postpones-us-tour-over-heartbreaking-loss-of-liam-payne-3804342">由于佩恩去世，马利克推迟了他的美国巡演</a>。这些演出将于一月份举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-earn-biggest-streaming-day-of-all-time-following-liam-paynes-death-3804388">利亚姆·佩恩去世后，《One Direction》的帖子创下了有史以来流媒体播放量最高的一天，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
